quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  27,64,"“Kapena (wabwino) ndiamene adayambitsa zolengedwa, (ndipo) kenako adzazibweza, kapenanso amene amakupatsani rizq (chakudya) kuchokera kumwamba ndi m’nthaka? Kodi pamodzi ndi Allah pali mulungu winanso? Nena: “Bweretsani umboni wanu ngati mukunena zoona (wotsimikizira kuti Allah ali ndi mnzake).”"
  27,65,"“Nena: “Palibe amene alipo kumwamba ndi pansi akudziwa zam’seri (zomwe zisanadze) kupatula Allah basi. Ndipo (amene akuwapembedza) sadziwa kuti ndiliti adzaukitsidwa ku imfa.”"
  27,66,“Kwakhwima liti kudziwa kwawo (za kudza) kwa tsiku la chimaliziro? Koma iwo ali mchikaiko ndi za tsikulo; koma iwo ngakhungu pa zatsikulo
  27,67,"“Ndipo adanena omwe adatsutsa (za Allah): “Kodi tikadzakhala dothi, ife ndi makolo athu akale, (nzoona) tidzatulutsidwanso (m’manda tili amoyo)?”"
  27,68,"“Ndithu tidalonjezedwa izi, ife ndi makolo athu kale, izi sichina koma ndi nthano (zabodza) za anthu akale.”"
  27,69,"“Nena: “Yendani pa dziko ndi kuona momwe adalili mapeto a oipa.”"
  27,70,"“Ndipo usawadandaulire, ndiponso usakhale wobanika chifukwa cha ziwembu zomwe akuchita"
  27,71,"“Ndipo (iwo) akuti: “Kodi lonjezoli lidzachitika liti, ngati mukunena zoona?”"
  27,72,"“Nena: “Kapena zina mwa zomwe mukuzifulumizitsa zili pafupi kukupezani.”"
  27,73,“Ndipo ndithu Mbuye wako ndi mwini kupereka ubwino (waukulu) kwa anthu; koma ambiri a iwo sathokoza
  27,74,“Ndipo ndithu Mbuye wako akudziwa zomwe zikubisa zifuwa zawo ndi zomwe akuonetsera poyera
  27,75,“Ndiponso palibe chobisika kumwamba ndi m’nthaka koma chili m’buku lofotokoza chilichonse
  27,76,"“Ndithu Qur’an iyi, ikufotokoza kwambiri za ana a Israyeli pa zambiri zomwe iwo akutsutsana"